snippet.title: Grounded Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Obsidian Entertainment reveals an all new story trailer for Grounded, their upcoming survival adventure game. On July 28th, go big or never go home. An Xbox Game Preview title built with community feedback and premiering on Xbox Game Pass for console and PC.

Learn more at https://www.xbox.com/games/grounded
